{"tid":2125161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林正財：政府豁免海員檢疫是出於人道立場 可惜船員不遵守要求","createTime":"2020-07-26T04:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T03:07:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":276,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec327f0b1350d963b3451846cd5f6b1d81f8978","tid":2125161,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:06:25.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員林正財在一個電視節目上表示，特區政府豁免來港海員檢疫，是出於人道立場，容許持續工作多月的海員在本港換班，但本月初發現有漏洞，於是要求海員在出發地先作病毒檢測，船公司亦答應會要求船員不出市區，可惜有人不遵守要求。 <br />\n<br />\n被問到政府是否「好心做壞事」，林正財表示疫情不斷演進，政府會實事求是調控措施，又指現時本港防疫工作遇到瓶頸，市民要求每個防疫程序都要做到滴水不漏，相關部門面對好大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348995&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=1c85f33a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348995</a>"},{"pid":"302be4d02c489b62fda39cd8be880671b09e87b4","tid":2125161,"uid":3860,"like":159,"dislike":1,"score":158,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"之前又話唔係漏洞<br />\n個發言人發假消息唔拉?"},{"pid":"1560910b36f598e8357be827d8fc827d84728614","tid":2125161,"uid":3241,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"林匪正財 咁邊個要負責， 果個人自殺左未<br />\n佢害死左幾個香港人喎<br />\n你地係兇手， 係殺人犯"},{"pid":"e47c79d5f3ce2a176eccb2c314484a77066d27ad","tid":2125161,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e433335f9a6b99346c5a30b335f12e0bf59f89d","tid":2125161,"uid":129664,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"人道立場，就係不人道對待香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3431c378bfb9708abd54aa420a57de98772ed8ea","tid":2125161,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":